  "frontCover": "Front cover of a birthday greeting card, featuring a humorous and chaotic scene with three stylized cartoon characters in medieval-inspired attire, reminiscent of classic animated films. The overall art style is flat 2D with bold outlines and a vibrant, limited color palette of blues, yellows, and flesh tones. A large banner at the top reads \"HAPPY BIRTHDAY, CRAIG!\" in bold, slightly distressed orange lettering, attached by blue ribbon. The character on the left, with brown hair and a stern expression, is struggling to inflate a yellow balloon animal. The character in the center, with blonde hair and a regal blue cape, looks bewildered while holding a tangled blue ribbon. The character in the foreground, with brown hair and a concerned expression, is carrying a tall, tiered birthday cake with lit candles. Scattered yellow balloons and blue confetti add to the festive, albeit slightly disorganized, atmosphere. The background is a solid royal blue. The composition is dynamic and full of character.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a birthday greeting card, a simple and cohesive closing to the story. The art style remains flat 2D with bold outlines and the same color palette. It features a stylized, whimsical arrangement of blue ribbons and a few scattered yellow confetti shapes, subtly referencing elements from the front cover. The design is clean and minimalist, providing a peaceful and artistic conclusion without any text or characters. The composition is balanced and visually appealing, echoing the overall theme and tone of the card.",
