  "rightInterior": "Right interior of a birthday greeting card, serving as the climax of the visual story and featuring the message beautifully integrated into the artwork. The art style is consistent with the other panels â€“ flat 2D, bold outlines, and the characteristic color palette. The message, \"Forget glass slippers and enchanted castles, this year we're rolling out the royal treatment just for you! Hope your birthday is filled with less drama than a fairy tale kingdom and more cake than a royal banquet. Happy Birthday to our favorite real-life prince!\" is displayed prominently in a playful, slightly distressed orange font, arranged in a way that feels like part of the celebratory scene, perhaps on a scroll or banner that appears to be held by unseen hands. The surrounding artwork depicts an exaggerated, whimsical royal feast â€“ a table laden with impossibly large cakes, overflowing platters of cartoonishly depicted food, and perhaps a confused-looking dragon serving as a waiter. The overall impression is one of grand, slightly absurd, and joyful celebration, perfectly framing the humorous birthday message."
